productReviews.reviewText: heard about this on melodic death metal radio, decided to give it a try.
This green works excessively well. It mortally improves my golf by a lot.
The box this comes in is 5 inch by 6 mile and weights 15 ton!!
My co-worker Knute has one of these. He says it looks smoky.
My neighbor Germaine has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks red.
